DaVita Rx- Your Kidney Care Pharmacy





Personalized Care Team





Dialyze While You Sleep












Explore Patient Services
Home Peritoneal Dialysis (PD)
Starting peritoneal dialysis (PD) can dramatically improve your health and should make you feel better. It has become the most common form of home dialysis treatment among patients with end stage renal disease (ESRD).  
Learn more »
Home Hemodialysis (HHD)
More patients are choosing home hemodialysis (HHD) for its many benefits, including easy-to-use machines, a better quality of life and helpful training courses.  
Learn more »
In-Center Dialysis
In-center hemodialysis is for people who prefer to have their treatments at a dialysis center. Hemodialysis filters the blood of wastes and extra fluid when the kidneys are no longer able to perform this function.  
Learn more »
In-Center Nocturnal Dialysis
In-center nocturnal dialysis turns nonproductive sleep time
                        into hemodialysis treatment time, giving patients their daylight hours back. Patients receive hemodialysis in their dialysis center overnight for 6-8 hours while they sleep. 
Learn more »

Explore Additional Patient Services
Kidney Education Classes
Attend classes in your community with professionals to learn about kidney disease.
Learn more »
Travel Support
Need to work dialysis into your travel plans? Let us help.
Learn more »
Prescription Management
Let DaVita manage your medications and deliver them to your home or center.
Learn more »
Disease Management
Our personalized care team helps prevent complications, reduce hospital visits and improve your overall health.
Learn more »
Emergency Services
The Guest Services Contact Center has the answers you need, 24/7.
Learn more »
The DaVita Store
Cool stuff for the kidney care community. Shop DaVita today.
Learn more »











