DaVita Culture





Leader in Quality Dialysis Care

												At DaVita, we're committed to improving kidney care. That's why we're proud that the government has rated DaVita highest among all major dialysis providers in its two key performance programs: Five-Star Quality Rating System and Quality Incentive Program (QIP).											









Want to leave a note for the CEO?

												Our "Mayor" and CEO, KT's office door is covered with Post-It Notes left by teammates.  This is one that we especially like!											







