 Contact Us
DaVita Guest Services
If you would like help locating a dialysis center, would like to become a DaVita patient or have comments about one of our centers, please call DaVita Guest Services.

Call us toll free at 1-800-244-0680(Operating hours: Mon.-Fri. 8:00 a.m. - 9:30 p.m. ET and Sat. 10:00 a.m. - 2:00 p.m. ET)

DaVita World Headquarters 

DaVita2000 16th St.Denver, CO 80202Phone: (303) 405-2100 or toll-free at 1-888-484-7505

Career inquiries

To learn more about working at DaVita, search for open positions in your area or to check on your application, please visit the careers section.
If you have technical difficulties while trying to apply online, please call our Career Hotline at 1-866-400-2266.

For corporate communications and media inquiries only
If you are a member of an accredited media organization and need to speak to a DaVita Media Representative, please contact Skip Thurman, Senior Director of Communications.

Skip Thurman2000 16th St.Denver, CO 80202(303) 876-6610

Send us a message
Please note: We can't give you medical advice online. Every person's condition is unique and each patient requires a professional assessment before medical guidance can be given. Speak with your personal physician about your questions and concerns.

For all other feedback or questions, fill out our contact form.(Your message will be forwarded to the appropriate department based on the subject.)

Sponsorship Requests
At DaVita, we’re committed to engaging our local communities. If your organization is based in Colorado, please fill out this form. For sponsorship opportunities outside of Colorado, please contact your nearest DaVita business office from the list below.
