Factors associated with the progression of kidney disease:

Uncontrolled blood pressure
High glucose
Excessive use of pain medications
Smoking
Tests using dye
Obesity








 



More about the DaVita GFR Calculator
The DaVita GFR calculator uses the 2009 CKD-EPI creatinine equation, which is recommended by the KDIGO Clinical Practice Guidelines for Management of Chronic Kidney Disease.


